
Don't you ever wish your life was like a movie? Where everything is perfect? Where the guy always got the girl? Where your hair doesn't get wet in water?
Olivia Cruise wants that perfect movie life, she wants to direct what happens. Most importantly, she wants to find her Romeo to her Juliet. But after being brutally betrayed by her best friend and boyfriend, will her movie life ever have a happy ending?
When she meets Liam Nace, a runaway foster teen, will he be able to stay long enough to be her Romeo? Or will she never see that handsome stranger again?
Based on a true story